game.name: BFF Princess Career Photoshoot
game.description:
Hey girls! Here is good news for your favorite two beauties Rapunzel and Moana! They have just completed their college degrees and now looking forward to work. Would you like to guide them to select their profession and build their career? Join BFF Princess Career Photoshoot game and be prepared to help them to pick up the right career option! Remember they are the best friends so try to be careful while taking a career decision. Hurry up! They are waiting for the fresh looks of their trial photoshoot.

Which career option out of Police, Nurse and Business Women you want to choose for your girl?  It will actually depend on your choice so no need to be based on anyone else. Your successful attempts will help princesses to secure enough points and get them ready for the photoshoot. Put your fashion abilities to the test to help both Disney princesses take the cool pictures in this one of the best HTML5 dressing game! Choose police option first and then help her princess get a perfect cop look! Dress her up with a nice black shirt and paint and complete her look with a cap and a pair of long shoes! 

Once it is done, click the picture and save it for your further use. Try to complete task fast as other princess Moana is also waiting for her turn! Give her the look of a businesswoman with the help of a plain shirt with coat and short skirt or with a professional jacket and paint! Complete her look with a cool hairstyle and combine it with a matching pair of sandals and handbag! Do not forget to capture her picture. You would see in the end that their pictures have got some nice comments and likes. Try out more girls dress-up games and have fun online without download!
